msgctxt "2840_Shizuka"
msgid "Um..."
msgstr "Em..."

msgctxt "2852_Player"
msgid "Thanks for waiting."
msgstr "Gracias por esperar."

msgctxt "2864_Shizuka"
msgid "If you have business with someone else, don't worry about me."
msgstr "If you have business with someone else, don't worry about me."

msgctxt "2876_Player"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "2888_Shizuka"
msgid "I'll be waiting here, so come back when you're done with whatever it is you have to do."
msgstr "Estaré esperando aquí, así que vuelve cuando haya terminado con lo que sea que tenga que hacer."

msgctxt "2900_Shizuka"
msgid "I'm glad you're safe. I started to worry when I didn't hear from you..."
msgstr "Me alegro de que estés a salvo. Empecé a preocuparme cuando no supe nada de usted..."

msgctxt "2912_Player"
msgid "Sorry for worrying you."
msgstr "Sorry for worrying you."

msgctxt "2924_Shizuka"
msgid "Um... Could I ask you something, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr "Um... ¿Puedo preguntarle algo, Kiryu-san?"

msgctxt "2936_Player"
msgid "Hm? Sure. Go ahead."
msgstr "Hm? Sure. Go ahead."

msgctxt "2948_Shizuka"
msgid "May I call you \"sir\"?"
msgstr "¿Puedo llamarle \"señor\"?"

msgctxt "2960_Player"
msgid "\"Sir\"? That's a bit too formal, isn't it?"
msgstr "\"Sir\"? That's a bit too formal, isn't it?"

msgctxt "2972_Shizuka"
msgid "You don't like it?"
msgstr "¿No le gusto?"

msgctxt "2984_Player"
msgid "Heh. Well... you can call me whatever you like."
msgstr "Heh. Well... you can call me whatever you like."

msgctxt "2996_Shizuka"
msgid "Really? I'm glad to hear you say that. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¿De verdad? Me alegra escucharlo decir eso. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "3008_Player"
msgid "You can be a bit strange sometimes..."
msgstr "You can be a bit strange sometimes..."

msgctxt "3020_Shizuka"
